Here Comes The Sun | Boho Rainbow Baby Shower Invitation – Baby Shower Invitations Boho Rainbow Baby Shower Invitation products are in stock Here Comes The Sun Try to read more firstHere comes the sun! Celebrate the arrival of your little darling with these boho baby shower invites. The front of the card features hand-painted watercolor retro typography with the "o" of "comes" as a sun. Below, there is a simple rainbow to separate the top from the event details. The event details are in a mix of classic serif and handwritten script fonts. The mom-to-be’s name is in big rusty red capitals, with the baby’s name in terracotta, the date is green, and the registry information is also in red. We have chosen an earthy color palette to match the boho style of the invites. The reverse features a hippie sun and rainbow pattern over a soft yellow color. Perfect for spring or summer celebrations. This simple design works for little boys, little girls, gender reveals, and gender-neutral baby showers. You can change the wording using the template boxes on the right of the design, or you can click on "Edit using Design Tool" to access the more advanced changes. Change fonts, colors, placement, size, and more. Message me through the button below if you need any help personalizing these cards. Please note I can’t modify an existing order so be sure to write me before purchasing! If you like this style but had something else in mind, I’d be happy to work with you on a custom order. More boho baby shower designs are available in our store! Price:$1.95
